ecting access to Google Drive and potentially the CMS](https://fathom.video/share/NNXKVsRCCq32UVBeeb8Mfh3cWWmmsK8G?tab=summary&timestamp=595.0)\n  - [Sydney submitted an IT request to address these restrictions](https://fathom.video/share/NNXKVsRCCq32UVBeeb8Mfh3cWWmmsK8G?tab=summary&timestamp=610.0)\n  - [Restrictions significantly impact workflow and productivity](https://fathom.video/share/NNXKVsRCCq32UVBeeb8Mfh3cWWmmsK8G?tab=summary&timestamp=618.0)\n\n### Access Management and Onboarding Process\n\n  - [Sydney recently gained access to Abnormal email (Tuesday of the meeting week)](https://fathom.video/share/NNXKVsRCCq32UVBeeb8Mfh3cWWmmsK8G?tab=summary&timestamp=475.0)\n  - [Removed from an exclusion list, causing temporary loss of Gmail access](https://fathom.video/share/NNXKVsRCCq32UVBeeb8Mfh3cWWmmsK8G?tab=summary&timestamp=687.0)\n  - [Communication breakdown: instructions sent to inaccessible Abnormal email](https://fathom.video/share/NNXKVsRCCq32UVBeeb8Mfh3cWWmmsK8G?tab=summary&timestamp=696.0)\n  - [Awaiting approval for Craft access from Jennifer (expected the following day)](https://fathom.video/share/NNXKVsRCCq32UVBeeb8Mfh3cWWmmsK8G?tab=summary&timestamp=717.0)\n  - [Sydney joined the Abnormal Slack channel last week](https://fathom.video/share/NNXKVsRCCq32UVBeeb8Mfh3cWWmmsK8G?tab=summary&timestamp=436.0)\n\n### IT Support and Communication\n\n  - [Jason advised Sydney to submit formal requests for access issues](https://fathom.video/share/NNXKVsRCCq32UVBeeb8Mfh3cWWmmsK8G?tab=summary&timestamp=660.0)\n  - [Discussed the process of requesting and approving access to tools like Craft](https://fathom.video/share/NNXKVsRCCq32UVBeeb8Mfh3cWWmmsK8G?tab=summary&timestamp=723.0)\n  - [Jason offered to send an email regarding Sydney's issues](https://fathom.video/share/NNXKVsRCCq32UVBeeb8Mfh3cWWmmsK8G?tab=summary&timestamp=765.0)\n\n## Next Steps\n\n  - [Sydney to follow up on the IT request submitted for Island restrictions](https://fathom.video/share/NNXKVsRCCq3